# How It Works

Claude Code auto-discovers all `.md` files in these locations at session start:
- `~/.claude/agents/` — user-scoped (all projects) ← your agents live here
- `.claude/agents/` — project-scoped (per repo)

No CLI command, config change, or restart is required. Files are picked up automatically.

